snippet.title: The Fellowship of the Ring gameplay (PC Game, 1986)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for The Fellowship of the Ring, Dos PC game produced by Beam Software in 1986 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/the-fellowship-of-the-ring/6182/
The game is divided into 2 parts. The first part starts with Frodo at his home in the Shire, where eventually you will team up with the other Hobbits Pippin and Sam. The second part of the game starts with forming of the fellowship.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Lord of the Rings - Fellowship of the Ring - https://youtu.be/lh-dWwbtRAQ
The Hobbit - https://youtu.be/1vpLgHV0pgk
Sram - https://youtu.be/PLfHtQnztqE
